{"tid":2179581,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得幼稚園老師易做既請入。強力建議入嚟望望","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:27:55.000Z","uid":360847,"like":19,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c843f08810c79562fa0a79f98a8a3ffa3fdaac7b","tid":2179581,"uid":360847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"成日話幼稚園老師陪細路，望住佢，教下ABC。<br />\n我想同你講老師係好多好多好多野做，重點要講三次。<br />\n小至小朋友傷左dd（可能撞到小小、傷到手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）大至佢開左大，你都要一一報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你記住你個班有至少30個人<br />\n無限咁多文件等住你交，寫兒童學習歷程檔案打到你手斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你每日翻工既時間係入班既時間，班務改簿你等你收工慢慢你改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改到2046<br />\n（改得太手緊又係你既錯，太鬆手都係你既錯）<br />\n手冊吸簿呢d工作，你千祈唔好出錯，吸印吸錯吸得樣衰就恭喜你，可以去校長到跪下玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會有第二本比你吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一切都係講功力<br />\n開會時間，好既會係翻工時間開，衰既你放工慢慢開，開足你一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六好既就3個鐘，唔好既翻全日啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放工時間？唔好講啦掛，實冇準時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校旅行兼任導遊同車長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡直全能<br />\n平日照顧d仔既時間係8至6可能7點都會架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餵飯、教書一腳踢，摩打手出動。<br />\n教細班腰都斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最重點係 時下家長會將所有責任推比學校，我個仔唔識係你教得唔好，係你既錯。呢一樣野係做老師完全冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為家長唔會覺得係自己冇跟進過小朋友既學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總知行行都有壞處，睇你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866757b8668be1e28e7b761518ea9e32dc3c2cb3","tid":2179581,"uid":328316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"準備出年HD grad之後乞食揮手區"},{"pid":"cb7b069ffc53c029f1b0e5cc3b229d2be6280b8a","tid":2179581,"uid":360847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"866757b8668be1e28e7b761518ea9e32dc3c2cb3","tid":2179581,"uid":328316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"準備出年HD grad之後乞食揮手區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"恭喜你，加入呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />努力啦，總會有出路，睇你運氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a30c8913e6efebaacd1c13e719ab4c699e71c6","tid":2179581,"uid":118647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"教書係咁 唔係邊有呢個價"},{"pid":"5a10fc5f1b24eae59583d9b7b6b5d54543d38725","tid":2179581,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"有心教呢行係好辛苦 特別啲新仔"},{"pid":"16726da808cde3d5527c4cb2846104a6e8604e83","tid":2179581,"uid":360847,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c4a30c8913e6efebaacd1c13e719ab4c699e71c6","tid":2179581,"uid":118647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"教書係咁 唔係邊有呢個價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"唔講以為人工好高，fg出嚟可能係既，做上去只係一份穩定既工作。揀得呢行都預左冇發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7434ffe8c88e25e253ac02d78ceb2a77fc9cc5","tid":2179581,"uid":237060,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:25:38.000Z","msg":"行行都辛苦㗎啦 睇下你覺得邊行辛苦少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6ab3770884e844a1671dfb837ee2dd205b00a7","tid":2179581,"uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"所以話<br />\n做中學老師最好<br />\n特別做band 3 學校<br />\n日日鳩hea<br />\n中學生又